<link href="./landing/faq.css" rel="stylesheet" />

<div class="faq-faq8 thq-section-padding">
  <div class="faq-max-width thq-section-max-width">
    <div class="faq-container10 thq-flex-column">
      <div class="thq-flex-column">
        <h2>
          <span class="faq-fragment6">
            <h2 class="faq-text20 thq-heading-2">FAQs</h2>
          </span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="thq-flex-column">
        <p>
          <span class="faq-fragment2"></span>
        </p>
        <p class="faq-text16 thq-body-large">
          Got questions? We've got answers.
        </p>

        <p></p>
        <div class="faq-list thq-flex-column">
          <div class="faq-faq1">
            <div class="faq-trigger1 thq-section-max-width">
              <p>
                <span class="faq-fragment1"></span>
              </p>
              <p class="faq-text15 thq-body-large">
                How does UCL Generator create personalized cover letters?
              </p>

              <p></p>
              <div class="faq-icons-container1">
                <div>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" class="faq-icon10">
                    <path d="M213.333 554.667h256v256c0 23.552 19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667s42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667v-256h256c23.552 0 42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667s-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667h-256v-256c0-23.552-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667s-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667v256h-256c-23.552 0-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667s19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667z" ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" class="faq-icon12">
                    <path d="M213.333 554.667h597.333c23.552 0 42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667s-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667h-597.333c-23.552 0-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667s19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667z" ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-container14">
              <span class="thq-body-small">
                UCL uses advanced AI to analyze your resume and the job description. It matches your skills and experiences to the job requirements, creating a tailored cover letter that highlights your most relevant qualifications. UCL ensures that key elements from both your background and the job posting are incorporated, resulting in a personalized letter that speaks directly to the position you're applying for.
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-faq2">
            <div class="faq-trigger2 thq-section-max-width">
              <p>
                <span class="faq-fragment3"></span>
              </p>
              <p class="faq-text17 thq-body-large">
                Will my cover letter pass through Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS)?
              </p>

              <p></p>
              <div class="faq-icons-container2">
                <div>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" class="faq-icon14">
                    <path d="M213.333 554.667h256v256c0 23.552 19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667s42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667v-256h256c23.552 0 42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667s-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667h-256v-256c0-23.552-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667s-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667v256h-256c-23.552 0-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667s19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667z" ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" class="faq-icon16">
                    <path d="M213.333 554.667h597.333c23.552 0 42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667s-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667h-597.333c-23.552 0-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667s19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667z" ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-container17">
              <span class="thq-body-small">
                Yes, UCL is designed with ATS in mind. Our AI incorporates relevant keywords and phrases from the job description into your cover letter, optimizing it for ATS screening. This increases the likelihood that your application will successfully pass through automated filters and reach human recruiters.
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-faq3">
            <div class="faq-trigger3 thq-section-max-width">
              <p>
                <span class="faq-fragment4"></span>
              </p>
              <p class="faq-text18 thq-body-large">
                Can I edit the cover letter after it's generated?
              </p>

              <p></p>
              <div class="faq-icons-container3">
                <div>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" class="faq-icon18">
                    <path d="M213.333 554.667h256v256c0 23.552 19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667s42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667v-256h256c23.552 0 42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667s-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667h-256v-256c0-23.552-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667s-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667v256h-256c-23.552 0-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667s19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667z" ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" class="faq-icon20">
                    <path d="M213.333 554.667h597.333c23.552 0 42.667-19.115 42.667-42.667s-19.115-42.667-42.667-42.667h-597.333c-23.552 0-42.667 19.115-42.667 42.667s19.115 42.667 42.667 42.667z" ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-container20">
              <span class="thq-body-small">
                Absolutely! While our AI creates a strong foundation for your cover letter, we understand the importance of adding your personal touch. After generation, you can use our built-in editor to modify any part of the letter. You can add, remove, or rephrase content to ensure the letter truly represents your voice and addresses any specific points you want to emphasize.
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="faq-text14 thq-body-large">
          If you don't find what you're looking for, feel free to contact us.
        </p>
        
        <button class="faq-button thq-button-outline">
          <span>
            <span class="faq-fragment5">
              <span class="thq-body-small"><%= link_to 'Contact Us', contact_us_path %></span>
            </span>
          </span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
